What value is returned by the following call?

```java
public static int bSearch(int[] a, int target) {
    int lo = 0, hi = a.length - 1;
    while (lo <= hi) {
        int mid = (lo + hi) / 2;
        if (a[mid] == target) return mid;
        else if (a[mid] < target) lo = mid + 1;
        else hi = mid - 1;
    }
    return -1;
}
```

