Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int[] a = {5, 2, 8, 1, 9};
for (int j = 0; j < a.length - 1; j++)
{
    int minIndex = j;
    for (int k = j + 1; k < a.length; k++)
    {
        if (a[k] < a[minIndex])
            minIndex = k;
    }
    int temp = a[j];
    a[j] = a[minIndex];
    a[minIndex] = temp;
}
System.out.println(a[0] + " " + a[1] + " " + a[2]);
```

